got two more of my sheep.

91
00:13:38,851 --> 00:13:40,487
Ah, that's bad.

92
00:13:40,822 --> 00:13:42,545
- It's been happening everywhere lately.
- You're right.

93
00:13:42,655 --> 00:13:46,439
