where I found him.

134
00:17:22,875 --> 00:17:25,318
- Oh, really?
- Uh-huh.

135
00:17:25,353 --> 00:17:27,141
Only wolves live in caves.

136
00:17:28,614 --> 00:17:29,979
But I found him.

137
00:17:32,751 --> 00:17:34,776
