00:17:45,264 --> 00:17:47,828
If you'd said no then it'd be easier now.

140
00:17:49,768 --> 00:17:51,032
It could be destiny,

141
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:54,511
and maybe that's why
he came to us right now.

142
00:18:23,602 --> 00:18:24,762
