we'll start getting ready for the move, all right?

145
00:20:48,547 --> 00:20:49,514
All right.

146
00:20:53,652 --> 00:20:56,177
Do you need anything from town?
Flour or rice?

147
00:20:57,089 --> 00:21:00,688
